killing everyone.

3
00:00:06.506 --> 00:00:07.809
needing to protect me

4
00:00:07.842 --> 00:00:09.342
<i>after all we've been through.</i>

5
00:00:11.979 --> 00:00:13.948
<i>- It's not safe for him</i>
<i>to be around my children.</i>

6
00:00:13.981 --> 00:00:16.449
