joint custody of our children.

7
00:00:16.483 --> 00:00:18.085
<i>- It's Diana.</i>
<i>Miranda's attorney.</i>

8
00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:19.187
<i>She's gone AWOL.</i>

9
00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:21.421
