with the kids.

35
00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:58.886
- You mean she abducted them?

36
00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.187
- Tomato. to-mah-to.

37
00:02:00.221 --> 00:02:01.822
All I know is.
she doesn't make a 2:00

