with my pants too.

57
00:02:34.855 --> 00:02:36.023
<i>- You got carjacked?</i>

58
00:02:36.057 --> 00:02:37.091
- Yeah.

59
00:02:37.124 --> 00:02:38.225
I'm not proud about it.

60
00:02:38.259 --> 00:02:39.927
These guys were
definitely pros.

61
00:02:39.961 --> 00:02:41.795
They had me boxed in
before I could even think.

62
00:02:41.829 --> 00:02:43.998
