103
00:04:06.914 --> 00:04:08.049
- You are literally
not the boss of us.

104
00:04:08.082 --> 00:04:09.649
- I will find a way.

105
00:04:09.682 --> 00:04:12.253
- You know. I'm in the shop
with Lucy all day today.

106
00:04:12.286 --> 00:04:13.854
I could just simply ask her
what kind of ring

107
00:04:13.888 --> 00:04:15.189
