in a subtle way.

108
00:04:15.222 --> 00:04:16.623
- No. absolutely not.

109
00:04:16.656 --> 00:04:17.892
Then she'll know
I'm gonna propose.

110
00:04:17.925 --> 00:04:19.894
- Look. Sarge. I can make this
so much easier for you. okay?

111
00:04:19.927 --> 00:04:21.195
