- Sure. yeah.

231
00:07:59.880 --> 00:08:01.348
Why don't we do some
online research at lunch?

232
00:08:01.382 --> 00:08:03.517
- Yeah. I'll send you
some links.

233
00:08:03.550 --> 00:08:04.985
