<i>- I think Rodge is</i>
<i>getting ready to propose.</i>

235
00:08:11.058 --> 00:08:12.226
<i>- Wow.</i>
<i>- Uh-huh.</i>

236
00:08:12.259 --> 00:08:13.627
<i>- Really?</i>
<i>- Yeah.</i>

237
00:08:13.661 --> 00:08:14.928
<i>I mean. like. the other day.</i>
<i>he brought up diamond rings.</i>

238
